# Project Direction

- Read `MANIFEST.md` before making architecture-shaping decisions.
- Treat the repository as a long-term framework repository, not a throwaway script folder.
- Keep the project **tab-first** (tabs/notation as product story), REAPER-first, deterministic-first and human-review-first.
- Preserve the canonical score model as source-agnostic and REAPER-agnostic; treat interchange formats (e.g. MusicXML) as adapters/bridges, not the product headline.
- Keep screenshot ingestion secondary and isolated from the structured-core path.
